data.description: This is the one you've been searching for! You simply won't find more living space for this price in Mehlville School District! This meticulously maintained, 2 story townhome is the perfect place for anyone needing a great layout & that's ready for your personal touches! There is a bedroom and a full bathroom on the main level, making this the perfect layout for anyone sharing this with family members that don't do stairs or anyone wanting space to spread out! The 2nd & 3rd bedrooms (upstairs) share the 2nd full bath, and each have their own benefits: The massive primary bedroom has a walk-in closet AND a large additional closet inside a connected vanity room. The 3rd bedroom has sliding glass doors that lead to the covered balcony & a massive closet that runs the length of the entire room! All newer modern appliances stay with the home! You'll love all of the natural light, hardwood floors, spacious rooms & amenities (pool, gym, etc.). Seller is offering a $2k credit to the buyer!
